{"tid":1909850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB : 港台時段取消後將延長「六點半新聞報道」至一小時","createTime":"2020-03-04T09:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T09:28:57.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cbb4aec38e7738756b4f3b57fc37f4555f739e50","tid":1909850,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:07:19.000Z","msg":"無綫電視上月向通訊局提出要求，希望免除播放港台節目。通訊局今日正式宣布，撤銷向免費電視發出須播放港台節目的指示，意味未來 TVB 及 ViuTV 將毋須播放，包括《頭條新聞》等在內港台節目。通訊局稱新措施是要更有效地運用頻譜和廣播時間，並指港台對免除要求無異議。TVB 則宣布，收回時段將用作延長「六點半新聞報道」至一小時。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2900777126674555/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F2900777126674555%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIWWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=f6d070e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2900777126674555/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"9592585f2dfb6a6f0111350cc2d11f2a21462d99","tid":1909850,"uid":122110,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:08:41.000Z","msg":"Dllm冇人睇cctvb新聞呀"},{"pid":"99981bf3e32a27fccf21946be2c2fc2f5b99f1b8","tid":1909850,"uid":83582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:08:42.000Z","msg":"維穩多半個鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3569fc74158c1584c4d985fe978f35e8f61d0f21","tid":1909850,"uid":114097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:09:18.000Z","msg":"哇屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a984de10f90c5a9fe302b6fa566e2640bd992e","tid":1909850,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:09:35.000Z","msg":"lihk仔 : <br />\n唔會去佢啲廣告商度洗板,冇事"},{"pid":"b013e6e57c432a7d3d9e2b027d3bc92588100766","tid":1909850,"uid":273703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:10:27.000Z","msg":"佢得新聞 11-12 點收視，但平時播港台 4-5點收視，比無線播多半個鐘明顯利益輸